com.sinovoice.hcicloudsdk.recorder
接口 ASRRecorderListener

public interface ASRRecorderListener

ASR录音机监听器，用于接收ASR录音机事件

ASR录音机初始化时传入监听器，见ASRCommonRecorder.init(String, ASRRecorderListener)
